quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"E re: “Ke senoletsoe hore sehlopha sa Li-jinn li ne li thehile tsebe ho mamela[Qur`an], tsa re: “Re fela re utloile palo e babatsehang"
  72,2,"“E tataisetsa tokeng, re khotsoe ka hona: ha re na ho kopanya mong le mong le Mong`a rona"
  72,3,"“Bo phahame Botlotlehi ba Mong`a rona: ha A na molekane kapa mora"
  72,4,"“Ho ne ho ena le maoatla har’a rona, ba neng ba tloaetse ho buoa mashano a matala ka Allah"
  72,5,“Empa rea lumela hore motho kapa moea ha ba na tokelo ea ho bua leshano ka Allah
  72,6,"“Ruri! Ho teng batho, ba batlang ts’ireletso ho Li-Jinn, empa li ba ekelelitse phosong"
  72,7,"“Ba nahana joaloka uena, hore Allah ha ana ho tsosa ope bafung –"
  72,8,“Re ile ra leka ho phahlolla makunutu a leholimo; empa ra fumana le lebetsoe ke balebeli ba matla le malakabe a mollo
  72,9,"“Re ne re lula re larile, ho utsoa; empa ke mong le mong ea neng a leka ho mamela u iphumana a lelekoa ke lelakabe le chalametsang"
  72,10,"“Ha re utloisisi hore na kotlo e lebisitsoe ho boohle lefats’eng, kapana Mong`abona Urerilehobatataisatselengnepahetseng"
  72,11,"“Ho na le ba bang hara rona ba lokileng, ba bang ba fapane: re latela litsela tse fapaneng"
  72,12,"“Empa re’a tseba hore re ke ke ra ferekanya merero ea Allah, kapa hona ho Mo ferekanya ka paleho"
  72,13,"“Haele rona, re utloang tataiso, re amohetse mang le mang ea kholoang ho `Mopi oa hae ha ana ts`abo, ea qhekanyetso kapa bohanyapetsi"
  72,14,"“Hara rona ho na le ba ithobelang Allah, le ba tsoang tseleng ea toka. – haele ba ithobileng –ba nkile tsela e topileng"
  72,15,"“Empa haele ba tsoapohang, ke libeso tsa Mollo-oa-Lihele"
  72,16,"“Haeba ba ile ba tsitlallela tseleng, Re ka be Re ba sitisitse ka pula tsa matlopotlopo"
  72,17,"“E le hore Re ba behe tekong. Empa mong le mong ea tla kheloha khopolong ea Mong`a hae, U tla mo otla ka kotlo e mahlonoko"
  72,18,"“Libaka tsa thapelo ke tsa Allah: kahoo le se bitse ho mong kantle ho Allah"
  72,19,"“Nakong eo lekhabunyane la Allah le emang ho Mo rapela, ba mo opela hare ka bongata"